      "name": "1/2 cup all-purpose flour",
      "amount": "cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "1 tablespoon cornstarch",
      "amount": "tablespoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix the granulated sugar, salt, flour, and cornstarch together in a small bowl until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture into an air fryer basket lined with parchment paper for easy cleanup.",
    "Air-fry the crumble mixture for about 10 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Let it cool slightly before serving as a snack or dessert."
